description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Parvati purrs with a rating of 73, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 146, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Leverage for East, 8 for South, and 1 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40732-76812-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
